Headline: Ce plan...doit se mettre a la fin de la suite de l'Atlas Curieux mis au jour en 1715
Text:
Plan
From: Fer, Nicolas de. L'Atlas curieux. Paris, 1715.
At the top five illustrations showing the Crucifixion. On the margins and at the bottom the Route of the Cross is shown.
Insets: "Carte de la Terre Sainte...", showing Holy Land with the route which Jesus took through Galilea, Samaria, Judea and Egypt; "Plan de la Ville de Jerusalem", a plan of the ancient city after Villalpando;
"Plan du Temple de Solomon dans Jerusalem".
